+/*
+ * Copyright (C) 2020, 2022 CESNET, https://photonics.cesnet.cz/
+ *
+ * Written by Jan Kundrát <jan.kundrat@cesnet.cz>
+ * Written by Tomáš Pecka <tomas.pecka@cesnet.cz>
